snippet.title: Mohrta - TRAILER
snippet.description:
Coming 2025 - Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2881610/Mohrta/

Mohrta is a nonlinear FPS game blending action, exploration, and light dungeon crawling. Explore a vast selection of unique environments, slay an enormous cast of otherworldly creatures, and upgrade your arsenal of multifaceted weapons.
